		Sustainability Report 2016




			Download our latest Sustainability Report, ‘Responding to a Changing World’, which was published on 13 March 2017 and addresses our three key sustainability focus areas: harm reduction; sustainable agriculture and farmer livelihoods; and corporate behaviour.

Sustainability Report 2016 (4.9 mb) 



 

		Harm Reduction Focus Report 2016




			This report, published on 23 February 2017, looks at the way in which the business has embraced the need to offer consumers a choice of new products, and how we are championing harm reduction and its potential to have a dramatic and positive effect on public health.

